'''''Have You Seen Drum Recently?''''' yasohotse 1989<ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b79d97975</ref><ref>https://africa.film/have-you-seen-drum-recently-a-documentary-by-drum-photographer-jurgen-schadeberg/</ref>, ni film ikaba ikoresha amafoto aturuka muri ''Drum'' archives ikaba ivuga inkuru kinyamakuru n'inyandiko  ku buzima bw'umuco na politiki ya [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/Have_You_Seen_Drum_Recently/8468743</ref> .  Mu myaka ya za 1950, ''Ingoma'' yibanze ku birabura bo mu mijyi baba mu isi yiganjemo ivanguramoko<ref>https://theculturetrip.com/africa/south-africa/articles/10-of-the-most-controversial-films-from-south-africa/</ref>. Harimo ingingo zerekeye umujyi wa jazz umujyi w'ubugizi bwa nabi<ref>https://www.journeyman.tv/film/3007/have-you-seen-drum-recently</ref>, ibihimbano na siporo byerekanaga ibyiringiro, ibyifuzo no kwiheba byumujyi, umujyi wigishije abirabura<ref>https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/history-in-africa/article/africas-media-empire-drums-expansion-to-nigeria/6F12716179FE7050F0313CD1900914BE</ref>.

Iyobowe na Jürgen Schadeberg, iyi filime ikubiyemo amashusho ya Oliver Tambo nk'umunyamategeko<ref>https://www.journeyman.tv/film/3007/have-you-seen-drum-recently</ref>, Trevor Huddleston yerekanye ko yamaganye isenywa rya Sophiatown, Nelson Mandela wagaragaye mu bakinnyi bateramakofe, Chief Luthuli wegukanye igihembo cyitiriwe Nobel ndetse n'umuririmbyi Miriam Makeba<ref>https://streampriser.dk/film/471d6960-36c2-437b-800d-26779b5966e8/have-you-seen-drum-recently</ref> . Umuziki winyuma ushingiye kumuziki wo muri 1950, harimo itsinda rinini, jazz, swing, kwela na [[:en:Tin_whistle|penny whistle]]<ref>https://alchetron.com/Have-You-Seen-Drum-Recently</ref>.

